The '''PLAYgreen Festival''' is "the largest eco-experimental college festival" in the United States.<ref name="daily cal">{{cite news|last=Burns|first=Sarah|title=Campus Festival Encourages Eco-Awareness|url=http://www.dailycal.org/article/112144/campus_festival_encourages_eco-awareness|accessdate=1 March 2011|newspaper=Daily Californian|date=28 February 2011}}</ref> It aims to promote [[sustainability]] and [[environmentalism|eco-consciousness]]. It focuses on college campuses and collaborates with the "I Heart Tap Water" campaign.<ref name="Official Website">{{cite web|title=Main page|url=http://www.playgreenfestival.com/|publisher=PLAYgreen festival|accessdate=1 March 2011}}</ref>
